Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.86,0:01:47.99,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:100865,107997}{\i1}Mine Nozomi went on a journey\Nto discover the true meaning of music.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.99,0:01:52.88,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:107997,112885}{\i1}At some point she started to cry\Nin despair, but continued to sing still.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.88,0:01:55.05,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:112885,115054}{\i1}To sing is to feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.76,0:02:02.18,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:119767,122186}{\i1}A single drop of water\Nsoon becomes a small stream.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.18,0:02:05.98,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:122186,125982}{\i1}It flows endlessly like a river\Nthrough the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.98,0:02:11.90,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:125982,131904}{\i1}Nozomi's "Song of Heart" moved\None person, then another and another.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.90,0:02:15.65,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:131904,135658}{\i1}Before long she captured\Nhearts of many, many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.11,0:02:22.33,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:137118,142331}{\i1}But in the middle of her journey Nozomi learns\Nthat her father's health problems have recurred.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.33,0:02:27.38,Default,[title],0,0,0,,{TIME:142331,147386}{\t(3055,5055,3,\1c&H101010&\3c&H101010&\4c&H101010&)\fad(0,400)}— Episode 23 —\NThe Phantom Singer{NOTE:第23話\\Nまぼろしの歌手}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.39,0:02:43.85,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:160391,163853}Sun TV chief producer, Yoshii Yoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.35,0:02:47.60,Default,Yoshi Yoshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:165354,167607}I listened to your song, young lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.90,0:02:51.19,Default,Yoshi Yoshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:168900,171194}I must admit, it was fantastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.19,0:02:54.48,Default,Yoshi Yoshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:171194,174489}I've been doing this job for 15 years\Nand I've heard thousands of songs,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.48,0:02:57.32,Default,Yoshi Yoshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:174489,177325}but it is the first time I listened\Nto one that was so touching.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.32,0:02:59.99,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:177325,179994}Thank you, but I do not\Ndeserve this compliment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.57,0:03:08.37,Default,Yoshi Yoshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:181579,188377}Lately, the switchboard of our station receives\Nnothing but requests for the "Song of Heart".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.37,0:03:13.21,Default,Yoshi Yoshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:188377,193216}We were surprised, because no one seemed\Nto know the song, let alone the singer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.21,0:03:16.13,Default,Yoshi Yoshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:193216,196135}So I set off to look for both.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.13,0:03:20.72,Default,Yoshi Yoshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:196135,200723}My investigation brought me to the festival\Nin Arashiyama, where I stumbled upon you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.64,0:03:23.72,Default,Yoshi Yoshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:202642,203726}I'm going to be serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.72,0:03:28.10,Default,Yoshi Yoshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:203726,208105}I want you to go on my show. I'd like us to discuss\Nthe contract when we get back to Tōkyō.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.10,0:03:30.35,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:208105,210358}But sir, I…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.35,0:03:34.52,Default,Yoshi Yoshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:210358,214529}If you have something to do,\Nwe can have the meeting tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.23,0:03:37.03,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:215238,217031}Please wait a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.03,0:03:40.40,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:217031,220409}I'm very thankful for your offer\Nto appear on your TV show.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.03,0:03:43.66,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:222036,223663}But please let me think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.66,0:03:44.70,Default,Yoshi Yoshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:223663,224705}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.70,0:03:46.20,Default,Yoshi Yoshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:224705,226207}Think about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.20,0:03:50.37,Default,Yoshi Yoshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:227208,230378}{\i1}I had never met a newcomer\Nwho'd have refused to appear on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.37,0:03:53.38,Default,Yoshi Yoshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:230378,233381}{\i1}On the contrary, they all\Nwere dying to sign the contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.84,0:03:57.38,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:233840,237385}I'm sorry to disappoint you, but I really\Nprefer to think it through first. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.17,0:04:01.88,Default,Yoshi Yoshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:238177,241889}{\i1}It doesn't look like she's trying\Nto get her value up, at least not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.35,0:04:14.27,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:252358,254277}Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.48,0:04:16.19,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:254485,256195}Kazuo! Yuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.19,0:04:18.69,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:256195,258698}– Sis!\N– Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.69,0:04:20.07,Default,Mine Yuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:258698,260074}I'm so glad you're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.11,0:04:22.74,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:261117,262743}How's Dad?\NHow's he feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.74,0:04:24.57,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:262743,264579}He's fine. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.57,0:04:25.53,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:264579,265538}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.53,0:04:27.79,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:265538,267790}Yes. Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.79,0:04:29.95,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:267790,269959}Oh, thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.95,0:04:32.83,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:269959,272837}But how did you know I'd be here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.42,0:04:35.33,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:273421,275339}We got a telegram.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.33,0:04:36.42,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:275339,276424}Telegram?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.42,0:04:39.63,Default,Mine Yuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:276424,279635}It was from someone\Nwith a funny name, like…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.63,0:04:41.26,Default,Mine Yuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:279635,281262}The Gorillas?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.26,0:04:43.84,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:281262,283848}Whoa! The Geriras?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.84,0:04:47.14,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:283848,287143}Hige-san is very thoughtful.\NI have to thank them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.14,0:04:48.39,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:287143,288394}Okay, let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.39,0:04:50.35,Default,Mine Yuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:288394,290354}Hehe, hold your horses.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.06,0:04:53.35,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:291063,293357}There's one thing\Nwe'd like to talk about first.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.06,0:04:55.27,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:294066,295276}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.27,0:04:57.27,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:295276,297278}Why don't I explain it to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.48,0:04:59.73,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:298487,299739}Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.73,0:05:01.94,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:299739,301949}Welcome back, Mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.94,0:05:04.20,Default,Mine Yuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:301949,304201}He'll tell you everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.20,0:05:06.03,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:304201,306037}What's going on, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.03,0:05:07.74,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:306037,307747}Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.74,0:05:09.91,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:307747,309916}You don't have to worry\Nabout your family anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.91,0:05:14.37,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:309916,314378}Your brother, Fanni Moriyama,\Nhas returned to live with your family.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.75,0:05:16.96,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:314754,316964}Really? Fanni did?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.96,0:05:18.38,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:316964,318382}He's living at our house now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.88,0:05:23.76,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:318883,323763}Exactly. Your brother came back to the family\Nand offered to take care of all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.76,0:05:27.39,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:323763,327391}Too bad you didn't get to see\Nthe day of his arrival.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.72,0:05:30.26,Default,Mine Yuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:327725,330269}Mom and Dad cried so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.26,0:05:34.89,Default,Mine Yuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:330269,334899}Kuma-san was like always,\Nthen he whacked his back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.69,0:05:37.90,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:335691,337902}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.90,0:05:39.98,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:337902,339987}Ah, come on, don't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.98,0:05:42.90,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:339987,342907}You know I hate\Nto see you in this state.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.90,0:05:45.74,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:343908,345743}Sorry, Kazuo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.74,0:05:47.41,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:345743,347411}I'm just so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.99,0:05:51.24,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:347995,351248}You better do your best,\Nfor your brother's sake, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.99,0:05:52.83,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:351999,352833}I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.16,0:05:56.67,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:354168,356671}Don't cry anymore. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.67,0:05:58.33,Default,Mine Yuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:356671,358339}Here, Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.33,0:05:59.34,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:358339,359340}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.60,0:06:12.85,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:370601,372853}– For me, french fries.\N– For me, okonomiyaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.68,0:06:14.73,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:373688,374730}For me…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.73,0:06:17.14,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:374730,377149}Oh? Yoshii-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.94,0:06:20.40,Default,Yoshi Yoshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:377942,380403}Sorry to disturb you, Maestro.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.40,0:06:23.36,Default,Yoshi Yoshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:380403,383364}Please forgive me for this indiscretion,\Nbut I let myself follow you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.36,0:06:24.78,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:383364,384782}What brings you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.78,0:06:28.28,Default,Yoshi Yoshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:384782,388285}Looks like Mine Nozomi is your\Napprentice, or am I mistaken?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.28,0:06:30.37,Default,Yoshi Yoshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:388285,390371}You shouldn't hide her\Nfrom the public like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.91,0:06:33.37,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:390913,393374}I never meant to hide her.\NQuite on the contrary.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.62,0:06:37.87,Default,Yoshi Yoshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:394625,397878}I'll negotiate your contract with\NMr. Egawa. Is this alright with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.58,0:06:39.54,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:398587,399547}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.54,0:06:41.38,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:399547,401382}I'm leaving everything\Nto my teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.88,0:06:49.72,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:403884,409724}The fact that Yoshii-san himself wants you\Nis the best proof that you're a real singer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.72,0:06:50.76,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:409724,410766}Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.76,0:06:52.72,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:410766,412727}Huh, things are going well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.72,0:06:54.77,Default,Mine Yuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:412727,414770}I always knew you're very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.77,0:06:56.39,Default,Mine Yuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:414770,416397}Too bad you're a little big, Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.49,0:07:20.58,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:435499,440588}Yoshii-san is recognized as one\Nof the best producers around.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.58,0:07:26.26,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:440588,446260}There are few famous singers today\Nwho have made it big without his help.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.34,0:07:33.85,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:448345,453851}Besides, the music festivals he organizes are of\Nremarkable quality, one the best in the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.68,0:07:37.27,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:454685,457271}Are you sure you want\Nto turn down his offer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.27,0:07:40.27,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:457271,460274}He will surely make you a star,\Neven bigger than I ever could.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.27,0:07:43.86,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:460274,463861}I'm scared of becoming a star.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.61,0:07:48.49,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:464612,468491}When you were on a journey, you gradually\Ngrew to dislike the idea of becoming a star.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.49,0:07:50.03,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:468491,470034}I understand it better than you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.86,0:07:54.58,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:471869,474580}But what you sing is a real song,\Nin its truest form.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.58,0:07:56.74,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:474580,476749}More people should hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.74,0:08:02.67,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:476749,482671}The only way to let people learn of it and love it,\Nis to appear on mass media in one form or another.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.67,0:08:10.42,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:486675,490429}Just take your time to think it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.42,0:08:12.43,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:490429,492431}I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.06,0:08:24.69,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:501065,504693}{\i1}Mr. Egawa has made\Nsome great points.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.69,0:08:27.98,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:504693,507988}{\i1}But if I appear on mass media,\Nwon't I soon lose sight of myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.98,0:08:29.99,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:507988,509990}{\i1}Won't I get blinded by stardom?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.79,0:08:46.71,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:523796,526715}{\i1}Before long, I could get too busy\Nto even take any lessons.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.71,0:08:48.42,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:526715,528425}{\i1}Become a mass media's puppet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.42,0:08:49.67,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:528425,529677}{\i1}I don't want that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.67,0:08:52.05,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:529677,532054}{\i1}I still remember\Nmy promise to Nitta-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.05,0:08:54.09,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:532054,534098}{\i1}That in 10, 20 years…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.09,0:08:58.18,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:534098,538185}{\i1}No, that throughout my whole life\NI won't betray my ideals and stay true to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.27,0:09:01.43,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:540271,541438}Sune-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.39,0:09:04.06,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:542398,544066}Want me to turn it off?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.06,0:09:05.19,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:544066,545192}Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.19,0:09:08.44,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:545192,548445}It used to upset me,\Nbut I don't mind it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.53,0:09:10.61,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:549530,550614}Then you'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.61,0:09:13.15,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:550614,553159}I'm glad to hear it.\NYou've got it together now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.15,0:09:17.16,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:553159,557163}This means you can face the world of television\Nwithout worrying that you'll change in a bad way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.87,0:09:19.16,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:557872,559165}I wonder about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.66,0:09:26.17,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:559665,566172}There are many singers who become famous\Nwithout betraying their ideals.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.75,0:09:29.34,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:566755,569341}At first it'll be a bit difficult\Nnot to get carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.34,0:09:35.68,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:569341,575681}But I believe you have enough integrity\Nto remain the true singer that you have become.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.30,0:09:38.55,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:576307,578559}Why don't you even try?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.55,0:09:40.51,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:578559,580519}You have what it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.51,0:09:43.48,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:580519,583480}Yet you look like\Nyou want to run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.73,0:09:46.31,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:584732,586317}That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.31,0:09:48.19,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:586317,588194}I never said I want to run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.19,0:09:49.98,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:588194,589987}I'm sorry, but that's just\Nhow it looks to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.98,0:09:52.99,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:589987,592990}That you're just afraid\Nof any challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.99,0:09:54.99,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:592990,594992}You've got it wrong! I just…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.99,0:09:57.53,Default,Radio,0,0,0,,{TIME:594992,597536}{\i1}The next request is\Nfor the "Song of Heart".
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.53,0:10:02.04,Default,Radio,0,0,0,,{TIME:597536,602041}{\i1}However, it's a mysterious piece,\Nto which we don't even know the lyrics very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.04,0:10:05.16,Default,Radio,0,0,0,,{TIME:602041,605169}{\i1}From the students in Kanazawa\Nto 60 years-old elderly people,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.16,0:10:08.58,Default,Radio,0,0,0,,{TIME:605169,608589}{\i1}the requests for this song come\Nfrom rural areas all around the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.58,0:10:14.30,Default,Radio,0,0,0,,{TIME:608589,614303}{\i1}It is unprecedented in the history of our station\Nfor such a phantom song to have so big demand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.30,0:10:15.93,Default,Radio,0,0,0,,{TIME:614303,615930}{\i1}Who in the world is the vocalist?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.93,0:10:17.05,Default,Radio,0,0,0,,{TIME:615930,617056}{\i1}Where is she now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.05,0:10:20.18,Default,Radio,0,0,0,,{TIME:617056,620184}{\i1}Finally, when will her fans\Nget to see her in public?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.18,0:10:22.39,Default,Radio,0,0,0,,{TIME:620184,622394}{\i1}These questions remain\Nunanswered for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.39,0:10:24.06,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:622394,624063}{\i1}I have my own fans?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.43,0:10:28.10,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:624438,628108}Nozomi-chan, is it really alright for you\Nto let your fans down like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.19,0:10:37.45,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:634198,637451}I'm an egoist, I know. But still…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.61,0:10:43.87,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:638619,643874}If this becomes my full time job and I become\Na mass media's puppet, I'll betray what I stand for.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.87,0:10:45.45,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:643874,645459}Nozomi-chan…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.45,0:10:46.71,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:645459,646710}But I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.71,0:10:49.08,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:646710,649088}Sune-chan, I made my decision.\NI'll give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.29,0:10:52.29,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:650297,652299}I might get crushed\Nby the world of television.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.29,0:10:53.75,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:652299,653759}But that doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.51,0:10:57.09,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:654510,657096}I have to think about the people\Nwho are waiting for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.42,0:10:58.84,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:657429,658847}Nozomi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.84,0:11:00.05,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:658847,660057}I'll sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.05,0:11:02.97,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:660057,662977}I'll sing for the people\Nwho want to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.97,0:11:08.48,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:662977,668482}But the most important thing is that I will sing\Nto improve myself. I can't ever forget that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.48,0:11:09.85,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:668482,669858}Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.85,0:11:11.73,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:669858,671735}Thank you. I'll need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.61,0:11:15.53,Default,Yoshi Yoshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:673612,675531}Hello? This is Yoshii.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.53,0:11:17.49,Default,Yoshi Yoshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:675531,677491}Ah, Mr. Egawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.49,0:11:19.57,Default,Yoshi Yoshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:677491,679576}Oh? Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.57,0:11:22.83,Default,Yoshi Yoshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:679576,682830}Do you really give consent for Mine Nozomi's\Nappearance on public television?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.83,0:11:24.20,Default,Yoshi Yoshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:682830,684206}I'm so thankful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.20,0:11:25.62,Default,Yoshi Yoshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:684206,685624}Oh, yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.62,0:11:27.75,Default,Yoshi Yoshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:685624,687751}Oh? A condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.16,0:11:31.67,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:688168,691672}She was thinking about it all night long\Nand seems resolved to go along with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.67,0:11:35.75,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:691672,695759}But I think it would be better if you discussed\Nthe conditions with her in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.55,0:11:38.59,Default,Yoshi Yoshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:696552,698595}Oh, you see, actually\Nit's a bit of a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.59,0:11:41.34,Default,Yoshi Yoshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:698595,701348}I'm flying to the United States\Nshortly after tonight's broadcast.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.34,0:11:43.26,Default,Yoshi Yoshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:701348,703267}I'll be away for entire two weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.05,0:11:46.81,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:704059,706812}That's fine, we can wait\Nuntil you get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.81,0:11:50.31,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:706812,710316}As a matter of fact, tomorrow\NI'm leaving for Europe myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.31,0:11:52.65,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:710316,712651}Let's meet in two weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.65,0:11:57.78,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:714653,717781}{\i1}I wonder if they'll agree to my terms.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.61,0:12:00.61,Default,Yoshi Yoshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:718615,720617}All right, everything went okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.61,0:12:03.78,Default,Yoshi Yoshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:720617,723787}{\i1}But I'd like to know\Nwhat her conditions are.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.53,0:12:09.04,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:724538,729043}Your request may be quite difficult for him,\Nbut I think he should agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.04,0:12:10.16,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:729043,730169}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.16,0:12:12.54,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:730169,732546}You must think only of singing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.54,0:12:14.59,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:732546,734590}Yes. I understand.
Comment: 0,0:12:21.84,0:12:21.84,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:741847,741847}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.63,0:12:23.97,Default,Worker,0,0,0,,{TIME:742639,743974}Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.97,0:12:24.85,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:743974,744850}Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.80,0:12:27.10,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:745809,747102}Good work!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.10,0:12:32.35,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:750105,752358}Today it took you longer than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.98,0:12:37.07,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:752983,757071}I didn't feel well today.\NIt was difficult for me to sing it the right way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.07,0:12:38.48,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:757071,758489}Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.48,0:12:39.86,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:758489,759865}Yes, just a little tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.32,0:12:42.91,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:761325,762910}Miki…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.91,0:12:44.91,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:762910,764912}You can't afford to relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.91,0:12:46.78,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:764912,766789}You have next performance right after.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.08,0:12:51.41,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:768082,771418}Five minutes of rest\Nwon't kill anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.96,0:13:02.93,Default,Worker,0,0,0,,{TIME:777966,782930}We still don't know who the singer for the\N"Song of Heart" is. What are we going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.93,0:13:07.26,Default,Worker,0,0,0,,{TIME:782930,787267}There's nothing we can do, to be honest.\NThe other companies are looking for her as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.26,0:13:10.77,Default,Worker,0,0,0,,{TIME:787267,790771}We don't anything about her\Nexcept that she's a cute young girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.77,0:13:13.56,Default,Worker,0,0,0,,{TIME:790771,793565}Really, a phantom singer,\Nfor lack of a better name. What a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.56,0:13:16.44,Default,Worker,0,0,0,,{TIME:793565,796443}Yes. A phantom singer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.86,0:13:19.61,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:796860,799613}"Song of Heart"? Surely not the one\NMine Nozomi had written?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.70,0:13:29.37,Default,Worker,0,0,0,,{TIME:805702,809373}{\i1}The one behind the "Song of Heart"\Nis truly a phantom singer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.37,0:13:31.12,Default,Worker,0,0,0,,{TIME:809373,811125}{\i1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.04,0:13:37.46,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:816046,817464}{\i1}It's Nozomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.46,0:13:41.71,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:817464,821718}{\i1}There's no mistake.\NOnly she could sing the "Song of Heart".
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.55,0:13:47.97,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:826557,827975}{\i1}This means…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.97,0:13:51.93,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:827975,831937}{\i1}At some point some recording company\Nis going to find her and she'll sing a contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.93,0:13:56.31,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:831937,836316}{\i1}"A phantom singer"? That name\Nis going to give her even more reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.94,0:13:58.86,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:837943,838861}Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.86,0:14:01.11,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:838861,841113}– It's me.\N– It's open.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.07,0:14:03.94,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:842072,843949}Miki, you're awake, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.94,0:14:05.78,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:843949,845784}What are you doing here\Nin the middle of the night?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.78,0:14:08.45,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:845784,848454}About the phantom singer\Nthey discussed about today…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.45,0:14:09.87,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:848454,849872}You mean Mine Nozomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.37,0:14:11.87,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:850372,851874}I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.87,0:14:13.50,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:851874,853500}Well, of course it's her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.50,0:14:15.04,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:853500,855043}You see, Mine…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.04,0:14:16.67,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:855043,856670}There's more?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.67,0:14:21.17,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:856670,861175}The chief producer Yoshii of Sun TV is planning\Nto put her on his next music festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.97,0:14:35.02,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:869975,875022}Mr. Yoshii's music festivals invite\Nonly the first-class musicians.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.02,0:14:39.77,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:875022,879776}And Mine Nozomi is making her debut\Non one of these festivals.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.77,0:14:41.11,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:879776,881111}Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.11,0:14:42.65,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:881111,882654}Yes, I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.53,0:14:48.74,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:885532,888744}She didn't release a single disc,\Nyet she's ahead of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.24,0:14:52.78,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:891246,892789}But listen to me, Miki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.78,0:14:55.00,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:892789,895000}The negotiations for her\Ncontract are postponed
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.00,0:14:58.12,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:895000,898128}until Yoshii-san comes back\Nfrom the United States.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.62,0:15:01.63,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:898629,901632}From what I know, Mine Nozomi\Nhas a condition on her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.21,0:15:03.13,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:902216,903133}A condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.09,0:15:07.55,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:904092,907554}It means that we have some space.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.55,0:15:09.01,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:907554,909014}Some space?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.01,0:15:11.72,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:909014,911725}Yes. Space to take\Nour own measures.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.72,0:15:15.14,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:911725,915145}Mom! I can always count on you.\NCan you really do something about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.35,0:15:22.65,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:916355,922653}Yes. You know that it is out of the question for\Nthe Kōda family to be left behind by the poor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.65,0:15:23.65,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:922653,923654}Mom…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.65,0:15:29.15,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:925656,929159}{\fad(0,1000)}The singer behind the\N"Song of Heart": Mine Nozomi{NOTE:心の唄歌手峰のぞみ}
Dialogue: 1,0:15:28.24,0:15:31.16,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:928242,931161}{\fad(1000,0)}It's Mine Nozomi, no mistake!{NOTE:峰のぞみと判明}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.09,0:15:47.09,Default,Reporter,0,0,0,,{TIME:945092,947094}Why were you in the shadows so far?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.09,0:15:48.47,Default,Reporter,0,0,0,,{TIME:947094,948470}Where you have been all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.47,0:15:50.22,Default,Reporter,0,0,0,,{TIME:948470,950222}Can you sing for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.51,0:15:52.34,Default,Scout,0,0,0,,{TIME:950514,952349}We'd love to sign\Na contract with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.34,0:15:54.18,Default,Scout,0,0,0,,{TIME:952349,954184}Oh, please consider our offer first.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.18,0:15:56.56,Default,Scout,0,0,0,,{TIME:954184,956562}We can guarantee exclusive\Nlate-night broadcasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.56,0:15:58.60,Default,Scout,0,0,0,,{TIME:956562,958605}And we can put you\Non our morning show.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.06,0:16:01.60,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:959064,961608}I really don't know what to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.61,0:16:06.82,Default,Reporter,0,0,0,,{TIME:963610,966822}Hello? This is Everything Sport.\NOh, it's you, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.82,0:16:08.94,Default,Reporter,0,0,0,,{TIME:966822,968949}Thank you again for the scoop\Nyou gave us the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.94,0:16:10.70,Default,Reporter,0,0,0,,{TIME:968949,970701}Mine Nozomi's conditions?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.70,0:16:12.49,Default,Reporter,0,0,0,,{TIME:970701,972494}She has her terms\Nregarding her debut?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.49,0:16:14.12,Default,Reporter,0,0,0,,{TIME:972494,974121}What? It's about contract money?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.12,0:16:18.20,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:974121,978208}Yes, yes it is. As a proof, the president\Nof the company promoting my daughter
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.20,0:16:21.29,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:978208,981295}prepared a contract for a heavenly sum\Nand sent the offer to Egawa Isao.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.04,0:16:23.63,Default,Reporter,0,0,0,,{TIME:982045,983630}Oh, you mean Uchida Productions?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.63,0:16:27.30,Default,Reporter,0,0,0,,{TIME:983630,987301}That's another big scoop. Thank you\Nfor your information and for choosing us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.96,0:16:34.30,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:988969,994308}{\i1}Even if they find out it's all fake,\Nit'll hurt her image nevertheless.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.89,0:16:39.18,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:994891,999187}{\fad(1000,1000)}The future of Mine Nozomi's contract\Nwith Sun TV depends on her conditions?{NOTE:峰のぞみ条件次第で太洋テレビ出演キャンセルか？}
Dialogue: 1,0:16:38.35,0:16:41.31,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:998353,1001315}{\fad(1000,0)}Uchida Productions\Nbegins to move aggressively{NOTE:内田プロ\\N積極的に動き出す}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.31,0:16:43.81,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:1001315,1003817}"A contract between\NUchida Productions and Mine Nozomi"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.81,0:16:45.90,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:1003817,1005902}"{\i1}The more money, the better{\i0},\Nsays the singer".
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.90,0:16:48.15,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:1005902,1008155}This is terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.15,0:16:51.95,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1008155,1011950}I didn't talk to anyone about it,\Nyet they wrote all of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.95,0:16:58.49,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:1011950,1018498}Yes, exactly. And even though there were people\Nfrom Uchida Productions, I never let anyone in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.49,0:17:00.91,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:1018498,1020917}And here they wrote that you\Nhave already signed the contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.96,0:17:04.67,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1021960,1024671}{\i1}Once Yoshii-san learns of it,\Nhe will be furious.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.67,0:17:06.92,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1024671,1026923}{\i1}Money's got nothing\Nto do with my terms.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.26,0:17:16.93,Default,Yoshi Yoshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1034264,1036933}I'm back. Here's the paperwork\Nfor her contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.93,0:17:17.72,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:1036933,1037726}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.14,0:17:23.64,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:1039144,1043649}I'd like to know who are you\Nplanning to broadcast this week?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.64,0:17:28.11,Default,Yoshi Yoshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1043649,1048111}Oh? I thought we talked about this\Nbefore I went to the United States.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.11,0:17:31.32,Default,Yoshi Yoshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1048111,1051323}I wanted to hold a special show\Nfor the singer behind the "Song of Heart".
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.32,0:17:33.78,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:1051323,1053784}Looks like you're not aware\Nthat Mine has turned on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.86,0:17:38.95,Default,Yoshi Yoshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1055869,1058955}What? "Mine Nozomi signs\Na contract with Uchida Productions."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.95,0:17:40.24,Default,Yoshi Yoshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1058955,1060248}"The more money, the better"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.33,0:17:43.58,Default,Yoshi Yoshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1061333,1063585}{\i1}So her terms were about the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.58,0:17:48.00,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:1063585,1068006}We no longer have the rights to use her, unless\Nwe sign our own contract with Uchida Productions.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.00,0:17:50.25,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:1068006,1070258}But it'll be a cold day in hell\Nbefore they sell her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.96,0:17:53.17,Default,Yoshi Yoshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1070967,1073178}{\i1}I… I can't believe that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.17,0:17:57.26,Default,Yoshi Yoshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1073178,1077265}{\i1}Was the singer behind the "Song of Heart"\Nsomeone of such a low moral character?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.14,0:18:01.93,Default,Boy,0,0,0,,{TIME:1080143,1081937}I'm sorry, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.93,0:18:04.27,Default,Boy,0,0,0,,{TIME:1081937,1084272}Could you pass us the ball?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.69,0:18:12.44,Default,Yoshi Yoshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1088694,1092447}{\i1}For me, the great Yoshii Yoshi,\Nto be deceived by some girl from the streets…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.24,0:18:21.66,Default,Yoshi Yoshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1097244,1101665}{\i1}Wait. If Mine Nozomi\Nwas really like that…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.66,0:18:24.12,Default,Yoshi Yoshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1101665,1104126}{\i1}What was that in Arashiyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.37,0:18:26.96,Default,Yoshi Yoshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1105377,1106962}{\i1}It wasn't fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.67,0:18:29.54,Default,Yoshi Yoshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1107671,1109548}{\i1}My ears can't be fooled.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.92,0:18:33.55,Default,Yoshi Yoshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1110924,1113552}{\i1}I'll talk to her directly.\NThat's the most important right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.60,0:18:51.31,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1128608,1131319}Thank you for arranging a meeting.\NI've been waiting for your return.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.07,0:18:55.82,Default,Yoshi Yoshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1132070,1135824}You don't have to care about the trash\Nthey write in the magazines, Mine-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.65,0:18:57.32,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1136658,1137325}Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.41,0:19:02.33,Default,Yoshi Yoshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1138410,1142330}It was a mistake on my part that I went\Nto America without listening to your terms.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.87,0:19:03.83,Default,Yoshi Yoshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1142873,1143832}So what are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.83,0:19:06.33,Default,Yoshi Yoshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1143832,1146334}Please name your terms now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.33,0:19:10.33,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1146334,1150338}I just want you not to force me to become\Na star at all costs for you to sell.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.67,0:19:13.80,Default,Yoshi Yoshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1151673,1153800}I see. What else?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.80,0:19:17.26,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1153800,1157262}I will do everything to be\Na true singer and not an instrument.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.26,0:19:19.05,Default,Yoshi Yoshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1157262,1159055}Anything more specific?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.05,0:19:21.60,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1159055,1161600}Huh? More specific?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.60,0:19:24.31,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1161600,1164311}I just listed my conditions.\NThat's all, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.89,0:19:25.81,Default,Yoshi Yoshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1164895,1165812}That's all?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.43,0:19:27.81,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1166438,1167814}Is it not good?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.81,0:19:30.06,Default,Yoshi Yoshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1168815,1170066}W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.06,0:19:32.31,Default,Yoshi Yoshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1170066,1172319}Y-Your only condition…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.31,0:19:34.86,Default,Yoshi Yoshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1172319,1174863}is just to not make you\Ninto a star at all costs?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.07,0:19:36.86,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1176072,1176865}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.61,0:19:39.40,Default,Yoshi Yoshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1177616,1179409}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.28,0:19:41.53,Default,Yoshi Yoshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1180285,1181536}So that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.53,0:19:44.87,Default,Yoshi Yoshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1181536,1184873}That's how it was. Ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.12,0:19:49.87,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1186124,1189878}Excuse me, but I don't think\NI had the right to be so upfront right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.96,0:19:54.38,Default,Yoshi Yoshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1191963,1194382}Very well.\NI agree to your condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.92,0:19:57.34,Default,Yoshi Yoshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1195926,1197344}However…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.34,0:19:59.84,Default,Yoshi Yoshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1197344,1199846}I hope you'll appear\Non our music festivals.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.63,0:20:01.59,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1200639,1201598}Naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.59,0:20:03.60,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1201598,1203600}I'll participate with great pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.90,0:20:18.28,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1213902,1218281}{\i1}Mine Nozomi wants to become a singer,\Nbut hasn't yet made her official debut.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.28,0:20:21.95,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1218281,1221952}{\i1}For you, it must be intoxicating\Nto feel so superior to Nozomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.95,0:20:24.87,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1221952,1224871}But your style is\Nnot so good, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.38,0:20:35.72,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1234389,1235724}Nozomi…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.72,0:20:37.51,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1235724,1237517}Mine Nozomi's on television!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.51,0:20:40.56,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1237517,1240562}That's not possible.\NWhat is she doing here? How?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.56,0:20:44.19,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1240562,1244191}She seems so happy\Nwhen she's singing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.57,0:20:51.36,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1248570,1251364}Damn you. Why do you always win?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.36,0:20:53.20,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1251364,1253200}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.99,0:20:59.49,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1254993,1259497}{\i1}Very well. I won't let it end like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.81,0:21:26.44,Default,Yoshi Yoshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1284814,1286441}{\i1}Mine Nozomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.44,0:21:28.90,Default,Yoshi Yoshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1286441,1288902}{\i1}You are a true singer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.90,0:21:30.98,Default,Yoshi Yoshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1288902,1290987}{\i1}My ears were right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.98,0:21:32.69,Default,Yoshi Yoshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1290987,1292697}{\i1}But know this, Mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.99,0:21:38.95,Default,Yoshi Yoshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1294991,1298954}{\i1}I'm not confident I'll be able\Nto meet the condition you set for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.95,0:21:43.87,Default,Yoshi Yoshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1300956,1303875}{\i1}You told me not to\Nmake you into a star…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.87,0:21:46.71,Default,Yoshi Yoshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1303875,1306711}{\i1}But would the world forgive me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.52,0:22:06.35,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1323520,1326356}{\i1}Nozomi sang.\NShe kept on singing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.35,0:22:09.31,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1326356,1329317}{\i1}To be heard by\Nas many people as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.31,0:22:13.32,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1329317,1333321}{\i1}Nozomi's song echoed\Nin the sky all over Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.19,0:22:15.19,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1334197,1335198}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.19,0:22:20.53,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1335198,1340537}I have very sensitive information about the\N"Song of Heart" artist and I want to make it public.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.53,0:22:22.83,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1340537,1342831}Yes. I'm waiting at Princess Hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.33,0:22:25.83,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1343331,1345834}I have informed\Nother companies as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.83,0:22:26.71,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1345834,1346710}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.71,0:22:28.46,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1346710,1348461}Who am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.46,0:22:32.09,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1348461,1352090}I'm the older sister\Nof Nohara Jun, the lyricist.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.71,0:22:36.21,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1354718,1356219}{\i1}Mine Nozomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.21,0:22:39.84,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1356219,1359848}{\i1}This time you'll get to taste\Nthe world of suffering I had to go through.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.80,0:22:42.30,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1360807,1362309}This time you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.30,0:22:43.89,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1362309,1363893}There's no mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.35,0:22:50.73,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1365353,1370734}{\i1}A lone woman, Nohara Michiko,\Nwho wishes for Mine Nozomi's misfortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.73,0:22:53.15,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1370734,1373153}{\i1}What is she planning?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.45,0:23:08.46,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1384456,1388460}{\i1}Not knowing about\Nthe cursed fate lurking over her,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.46,0:23:11.88,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1388460,1391880}{\i1}Mine Nozomi kept on\Nsinging innocently.
Comment: 0,0:23:26.34,0:23:26.34,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:1406344,1406344}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.45,0:23:32.16,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1407454,1412167}{\i1}Mine Nozomi appears on television\Nand her popularity begins to rapidly grow.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.16,0:23:35.75,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1412167,1415754}{\i1}There is one woman, however,\Nwho is not pleased to see her success.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.75,0:23:39.88,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1415754,1419883}{\i1}Nohara Michiko continues\Nher scheming to see Nozomi's fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.88,0:23:45.97,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1419883,1425972}{\i1}Michiko gathers press\Nand speaks out surprising facts.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.97,0:23:48.39,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1425972,1428391}{\i1}What does she tell them?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.39,0:23:52.93,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1428391,1432937}{\i1}Please look forward to the next episode:\N"The Secret Is Out".
Comment: 0,0:23:52.93,0:23:52.93,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:1432937,1432937}Ending
